na </PERSON> included the weapons list with his letter. `` I passed it on to Col. <PERSON> North </PERSON>,'' <PERSON> Miller </PERSON> said in his deposition. `` Mr. <PERSON> Pena </PERSON> asked me to pass it on to whoever the appropriate person was.'' <PERSON> Pena </PERSON> said nothing ever came of the offer. Asked if he had any personal contact with <PERSON> North </PERSON>, <PERSON> Pena </PERSON> said he had met him many years ago at an Organization of <LOCATION> American </LOCATION> <LOCATION> States </LOCATION> reception. <PERSON> Pena </PERSON>, who works for a <LOCATION> Washington </LOCATION> public relations firm, has not returned several messages left at his office in the past 11 days.
