ling a hostage deal. <LOCATION> France </LOCATION> released a terrorist suspect, <PERSON> Mohamed </PERSON> <PERSON> Mohajer </PERSON>, a Lebanese Shiite, on March 24. It cited insufficient evidence to hold him for involvement in a series of 1986 bombings. Officials denied at the time the release had anything to do with the hostage negotiations.
