<HEAD>Dukakis And Jackson Still Locked In One Battle As Next Begins</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: INSERTS 1 graf after 3rd graf to UPDATE Colorado returns.</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By EVANS WITT</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>AP Political Writer</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
