age 3, and Chancellor <PERSON> James </PERSON> <PERSON> Wharton </PERSON> said she might be used to breed <PERSON> Mike </PERSON> <PERSON> V. </PERSON> <PERSON> Rockhold </PERSON> is in no hurry to lose a pet or regain a bedroom. `` I'll just cry my eyes out when that kittycat is gone, just like any mother would,'' she said.
